ay 2011}}</ref>\n*[[EFL League One Player of the Month|League One Player of the Month]]: March 2010<ref name=\"Super Steve strikes again \"/>\n*[[Millwall F.C.#Player of the year|Millwall Player of the Year]]: [[2016\u201317 Millwall F.C. season|2016\u201317]]<ref name=\"Morison is your MSC Player of the Year!\">{{cite news |title=Morison is your MSC Player of the Year! |url=https://www.millwallfc.co.uk/news/2017/april/morison-is-your-msc-player-of-the-year/ |publisher=Millwall F.C. |date=20 April 2017 |accessdate=2 November 2017}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category}}\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20170529115834/http://www.millwallfc.co.uk/team/player-profile/steve-morison/20 Steve Morison profile] at the [[Millwall F.C.]] website\n*{{Soccerbase}}\n\n{{Shrewsbury Town F.C. squad}}\n<!-- {{Millwall F.C. squad}} -->\n{{Millwall F.C. Player of the Year}}\n{{Stevenage F.C. Player of the Year}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Morison, Steve}}\n[[Category:1983 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Footballers from Enfield Town]]\n[[Category:English footballers]]\n[[Category:England semi-pro international footballers]]\n[[Category:Welsh footballers]]\n[[Category:Wales international footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football forwards]]\n[[Category:Northampton Town F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Bishop's Stortford F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Stevenage F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Millwall F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Norwich City F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Leeds United F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Shrewsbury Town F.C. players]]\n[[Category:English Football League players]]\n[[Category:National League (English football) players]]\n[[Category:Premier League players]]\n[[Category:People educated at Enfield Grammar School]]\n[[Category:English people of Welsh descent]]\n[[Category:Articles containing video clips]]\n[[Category:Northampton Town F.C. non-playing staff]]\n", "name_user": "Robby.is.on", "label": "safe", "comment": "Condense reference